stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> pending: registerTenant\nTenantRegistered

  pending --> active: activateTenant\nchecksum bumped · cache invalidated\nTenantActivated
  active --> inactive: deactivateTenant\nTenantDeactivated
  inactive --> active: activateTenant\nTenantActivated
  pending --> inactive: deactivateTenant

  active --> active: resolveTenant\nbuild context (inheritance) · cache by checksum\nTenantResolved
  inactive --> inactive: resolveTenant (active=false)
  pending --> pending: resolveTenant (active=false)

  active --> suspended: update tenantStatus
  suspended --> active: activateTenant

  note right of active
    resolveTenant returns a frozen context:
    capabilities = defaults ∪ tenant,
    labels/config/policy = tenant-overrides-default,
    active = (status === active).
    Cross-namespace + cross-tenant access is prevented.
  end note

  note right of pending
    verify() recomputes each tenant's checksum;
    a mismatch → integrity issue (resolve throws IntegrityError).
  end note
